---
title: Bacon Wrapped Pork Chops Maple Mash and Mustard Beans
description: Pork chops are wrapped in salty, smoky bacon and pan-fried to create the juiciest pork chop you'll ever have! Maple mashed sweet potatoes and mustard green beans round out this pork lovers' dream!
